		(uuid "21d211e1-8b2f-44c9-9502-18edb2b2d4d2")
	)
	(text "Import my common USB shits?\n\nI don't really need to fuck with 24V power supply, this is a tech demo.\n\nMake it viable as a pi hat? place SWD + SPI? or UART? to the XMC on the hat pins?\n\nI mean, why not? it's a fun mode of operation?  Copy off my hat boards, those are proven out now?\n\nYou Still need _somethign_ to be some demo IOs for ethercat.\nDrop a can txer down too.  (I mean, bonus points for making it have a jbtmarel 24v can connector?"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 24.384 241.808 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "3b5fa067-7cdf-4ba7-8d9b-34a71512e6fa")
	)
	(text "TODO\n* Connect CAN shutdown to \"any\" free gpio (do late)\n* phy clock sel to \"any\" free gpio (do late)\n* Add \"somethign\" to be the on board periph?\n  => IOs? sensors?"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 118.364 -16.51 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.54 2.54)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "575b4943-ac6b-413c-abc7-8a006db1ad1e")
	)
	(text "Do I need CRS/COL for plain ethernet?\nI don't think so.  CRS/DV is combined on RMII, no-one uses COL?"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 182.372 109.22 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "6fc9d02c-5c4b-4712-b7ef-9ab986eba6bc")
	)
	(text "Free Signals to be placed at leisure when routing\n(But need to be placed!)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 26.162 31.75 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "caabd91d-db47-4995-bb13-c8aa3c8eab7a")
	)
	(text "In Ethercat, XMC48 needs to provide clock to keep in sync\nFor Ethernet, still need a clock for the phys!\nWe can't generate 25M with CCU81 on that pin,\nso mux a 25M oscillator.\n(OSC is default! pull down CLK_SEL to use ECAT!)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 212.852 200.914 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "edb8446b-c198-4763-837e-65d2a5102541")
	)
